	The NIC's view is that a "reasonable number" of nicknames
	for any host is normally ZERO.

Ken - I for one, and I suspect many of the others on this mailing list,
would appreciate a few sentences explaining WHY this is the NIC's view.
Perhaps if we understood the benefits of this policy we'd be a bit
more understanding.

	Mark

